drop table "BC_SpaceAdjustOldBooth" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "BC_SpaceAdjustOldBooth" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "BC_SpaceAdjustOldBooth"
(
"OldID" NUMBER(32) not null,
BCID NUMBER(32),
"StoreyID" NUMBER(32),
"BoothID" NUMBER(32),
"BoothCode" VARCHAR(20),
"ReallyArea" DECIMAL(20, 4),
"ShareRatio" DECIMAL(6, 2),
"BoothLevel" NUMBER(32),
"CategoryID" NUMBER(32),
"BudgetaryPrice" DECIMAL(20, 2),
"BoothDesc" NVARCHAR2(2000),
"CreatTime" TIMESTAMP,
"DoorplateRemarks" NVARCHAR2(2000),
constraint PK_BC_SPACEADJUSTOLDBOOTH primary key ("OldID")
);

comment on column "BC_SpaceAdjustOldBooth"."StoreyID" is
'不做外键，加速搜索索引';

comment on column "BC_SpaceAdjustOldBooth"."BoothID" is
'根据展位ID获取展位已有的异动方案列表时使用';

comment on column "BC_SpaceAdjustOldBooth"."CreatTime" is
'创建时间和展位编码确定原展位';
